<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 20:08:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列总检察长预计将对本格维尔的警察局长人选表示担忧，因为他涉嫌不当行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/ag-expected-to-raise-concerns-over-ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-amid-alleged-misconduct/00000190-7eb3-d08e-a3f8-7fb344c90000</link><description>高级任命咨询委员会就提名阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德为国家警察局长举行了第一次会议，但尚未做出任何决定。 2015年，《国土报》揭露了佩莱德在担任耶路撒冷区副司令期间的不当交易</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 18:02:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/ag-expected-to-raise-concerns-over-ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-amid-alleged-misconduct/00000190-7eb3-d08e-a3f8-7fb344c90000</guid></item><item><title>阻止拜登就意味着支持特朗普。它不会解放巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-04/ty-article/.highlight/blocking-biden-means-stumping-for-trump-it-wont-free-palestine/00000190-7e58-d08e-a3f8-7fd91acb0000</link><description>我们可能已经集体将特朗普时代从我们的记忆中抹去了，但如果他因为拜登在加沙的资历而被允许再次掌权，那么无论在国内还是国外，都会出现更糟糕的版本</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:47:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-04/ty-article/.highlight/blocking-biden-means-stumping-for-trump-it-wont-free-palestine/00000190-7e58-d08e-a3f8-7fd91acb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 272 天：以色列国防军军官在真主党火箭弹袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-272-idf-officer-killed-in-hezbollah-rocket-barrage/00000190-7e9c-d12c-ab9a-7ffe9f260000</link><description>真主党向以色列北部发射了 200 多枚火箭弹和 20 架无人机，作为对高级指挥官被杀的回应 ■ 高级消息人士告诉《国土报》，哈马斯对当前停火提议的最新回应是“迄今为止最好的” ■ 内塔尼亚胡批准谈判小组离开以继续停火会谈 ■ 以色列国防军表示，它袭击了近东救济工程处位于加沙的两所学校，声称这些学校被用作哈马斯总部 ■ 战争进入 272 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:45:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-272-idf-officer-killed-in-hezbollah-rocket-barrage/00000190-7e9c-d12c-ab9a-7ffe9f260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方调查耶路撒冷纵火案，引发火灾；两人受伤 居民疏散</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/police-investigate-jerusalem-arson-sparking-fires-two-injured-residents-evacuated/00000190-7e13-df13-a798-fed3a0b00000</link><description>消防人员在耶路撒冷吉洛社区与大火搏斗后，以色列警方调查了可能的纵火案。与此同时，以色列极端炎热干燥的天气条件下野火爆发激增</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:50:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/police-investigate-jerusalem-arson-sparking-fires-two-injured-residents-evacuated/00000190-7e13-df13-a798-fed3a0b00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长看到加沙协议的机会，但担心内塔尼亚胡会因政治原因破坏协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/defense-chiefs-see-chance-for-gaza-deal-fear-netanyahu-will-derail-it-for-politics/00000190-7df0-da1d-a19a-fdfcb9ef0000</link><description>在释放人质和政治生存之间，总理打算如何选择是显而易见的 ■ 安全官员担心内塔尼亚胡的立场可能会加剧黎巴嫩局势升级 ■ 如果公众不觉醒，就不会达成协议，战争将继续下去，并且可能会在多个方面加剧</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/defense-chiefs-see-chance-for-gaza-deal-fear-netanyahu-will-derail-it-for-politics/00000190-7df0-da1d-a19a-fdfcb9ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军军官被黎巴嫩的炮火袭击身亡；以色列国防军称超过200枚火箭弹和20架无人机瞄准以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-over-200-rockets-20-drones-fired-at-israel-from-lebanon-two-wounded/00000190-7e11-dff5-a5d2-7f717b300000</link><description>真主党表示，这些袭击是对以色列杀害真主党高级指挥官的回应，预计会出现“一系列反应” ■ 以色列北部多个地点在炮火袭击后爆发火灾 ■ 以色列国防军预备役军官被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-over-200-rockets-20-drones-fired-at-israel-from-lebanon-two-wounded/00000190-7e11-dff5-a5d2-7f717b300000</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 的流行趋势展示了流离失所的加沙人的生活。所有以色列人都应该观看</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tiktok-trend-shows-what-life-is-like-for-displaced-gazans-all-israelis-should-watch/00000190-7dc3-da69-adf5-7fcf05c70000</link><description>由于以色列的新闻节目没有展示加沙普通巴勒斯坦人的生活，加沙人自己发布的 TikTok 视频可能正是让以色列人摆脱冷漠和非人化的茧的原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tiktok-trend-shows-what-life-is-like-for-displaced-gazans-all-israelis-should-watch/00000190-7dc3-da69-adf5-7fcf05c70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列律师协会对称本格维尔为“恐怖分子”的阿拉伯律师进行纪律处分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bar-association-to-discipline-arab-lawyer-who-called-ben-gvir-a-terrorist/00000190-7d9b-d08e-a3f8-7f9b301a0000</link><description>一名右翼活动人士提出了申诉，并引用了阿迈勒·奥拉比的其他声明，奥拉比称以色列境内的巴勒斯坦被拘留者为“人质”，并赞扬了联合国秘书长批评以色列的讲话。他的律师称道德投诉毫无根据</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 13:38:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bar-association-to-discipline-arab-lawyer-who-called-ben-gvir-a-terrorist/00000190-7d9b-d08e-a3f8-7f9b301a0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日被杀的以色列裔美国人的父亲呼吁以色列和哈马斯接受人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/father-of-israeli-american-killed-on-oct-7-calls-israel-and-hamas-to-accept-hostage-deal/00000190-7d7f-dbb2-a3f0-fd7f97df0000</link><description>陈鲁比写道，“内塔尼亚胡似乎正在退出（拜登的）停火协议”，并补充说，内塔尼亚胡“应该把精力放在带我儿子回家上，而不是准备一场政治之旅，以赢得华盛顿的民心”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 12:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/father-of-israeli-american-killed-on-oct-7-calls-israel-and-hamas-to-accept-hostage-deal/00000190-7d7f-dbb2-a3f0-fd7f97df0000</guid></item><item><title>对以色列战争撤离人员的资助即将到期；政府尚未决定继续提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/funding-for-israeli-war-evacuees-set-to-expire-govt-yet-to-decide-on-continued-funds/00000190-7d5c-d835-a9fb-ffffde960000</link><description>财政部批准为北部流离失所的居民提供资金直至 7 月 7 日，在接到指示与真主党的冲突将于该日期结束后，寻求额外资金的努力引发了激烈的政治争论</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:50:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/funding-for-israeli-war-evacuees-set-to-expire-govt-yet-to-decide-on-continued-funds/00000190-7d5c-d835-a9fb-ffffde960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人真的想与真主党发生全面战争吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/do-israelis-really-want-full-scale-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-7d43-d5c3-a596-7d4f39800000</link><description>“我们只是在等待战争。”在街头和媒体上，以色列人似乎相信，与黎巴嫩真主党的全面战争即将来临。但民意调查显示公众意见存在分歧，生活在重大冲突前线的以色列北部的公众人物提出了发人深省的评估</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:16:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/do-israelis-really-want-full-scale-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-7d43-d5c3-a596-7d4f39800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡授予外交部长特别许可，允许其携带妻子参加所有由政府承担费用的海外旅行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-grants-fm-permission-to-bring-wife-on-all-overseas-travel-at-govt-expense/00000190-7d0a-d0b6-a9b1-7dfea3490000</link><description>外交部长获得了不同寻常的全面批准，可以与妻子一起旅行，费用由政府承担。一位外交消息人士称，“在这样的时刻，这是不必要的、令人愤慨的浪费金钱”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:48:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-grants-fm-permission-to-bring-wife-on-all-overseas-travel-at-govt-expense/00000190-7d0a-d0b6-a9b1-7dfea3490000</guid></item><item><title>本古里安机场预计夏季旅客人数激增，但仍低于战前水平</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/ben-gurion-airport-expects-summer-surge-in-passengers-still-below-pre-war-levels/00000190-7d33-d835-a9fb-ffbb2c030000</link><description>以色列机场管理局预计 7 月和 8 月将有 180 万名旅客乘飞机出行，而去年分别为 260 万人次和 290 万人次</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/ben-gurion-airport-expects-summer-surge-in-passengers-still-below-pre-war-levels/00000190-7d33-d835-a9fb-ffbb2c030000</guid></item><item><title>“一些法国犹太人会接受议会中的极右反犹太主义，因为他们相信勒庞会保护他们”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-04/ty-article-podcast/some-french-jews-believe-le-pen-will-protect-them/00000190-78c9-d7ff-a7b2-fbfb880b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:53:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-04/ty-article-podcast/some-french-jews-believe-le-pen-will-protect-them/00000190-78c9-d7ff-a7b2-fbfb880b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于争论持续存在，哈马斯对以色列提议的回应令消息人士持“乐观”态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/sources-optimistic-following-hamas-response-to-israeli-proposal-as-contentions-persist/00000190-7caa-d835-a9fb-ffbbad090000</link><description>一位以色列外交消息人士称，哈马斯并不坚持“全面停火”。另一位人士表示，内塔尼亚胡发布了一份官方声明，称该组织坚持停火和从加沙撤军是“不可接受的”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:33:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/sources-optimistic-following-hamas-response-to-israeli-proposal-as-contentions-persist/00000190-7caa-d835-a9fb-ffbbad090000</guid></item><item><title>本尼·莫里斯如何学会停止担忧并热爱炸弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/how-benny-morris-learned-to-stop-worrying-and-love-the-bomb/00000190-7908-d5c3-a596-7d4e0b050000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/how-benny-morris-learned-to-stop-worrying-and-love-the-bomb/00000190-7908-d5c3-a596-7d4e0b050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官在加沙北部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/israeli-officer-killed-in-north-gaza-fighting/00000190-7c2d-d5c3-a596-7d6fd1b10000</link><description>21 岁的罗伊·米勒上尉来自荷兹利亚，是纳蒂 (Nati) 和阿里埃拉 (Ariela) 的儿子。他的母亲说他的生日是下周：“我很幸运拥有 22 年令人惊叹的岁月，只剩下一周了”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:11:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/israeli-officer-killed-in-north-gaza-fighting/00000190-7c2d-d5c3-a596-7d6fd1b10000</guid></item><item><title>尽管以色列暗杀真主党高级指挥官，但平息黎巴嫩动乱的努力仍在继续</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/killing-of-its-top-figures-replaces-israels-strategy-in-hezbollah-conflict/00000190-7a16-d0b6-a9b1-7ff6cdc00000</link><description>以色列对真主党高级指挥官的暗杀看起来越来越像是战略成就的替代品，预计它不会比之前的战略更能改变指导真主党和伊朗的战略</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/killing-of-its-top-figures-replaces-israels-strategy-in-hezbollah-conflict/00000190-7a16-d0b6-a9b1-7ff6cdc00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军士兵在加沙城战斗中丧生；美国高级官员称人质谈判取得重大突破</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article-live/hamas-positive-on-cease-fire-talks-israeli-source-basis-for-progress/00000190-7b75-d5c3-a596-7f7fde080000</link><description>真主党向以色列发射 200 多枚火箭弹和无人机后，以色列国防军对黎巴嫩南部发动袭击 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在以色列北部的炮火袭击中丧生，据报道两人受伤；火箭坠落引发火灾 ■ 内塔尼亚胡与拜登总统讨论哈马斯停火提议 ■ 反政府抗议者封锁以色列中部高速公路</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article-live/hamas-positive-on-cease-fire-talks-israeli-source-basis-for-progress/00000190-7b75-d5c3-a596-7f7fde080000</guid></item><item><title>新调查驳斥以色列最初调查：1982年轮胎灾难是恐怖袭击，不是瓦斯爆炸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/new-inquiry-refutes-original-israeli-probe-1982-tyre-disaster-was-terror-not-gas-blast/00000190-7a17-d3cb-a7ff-fb7fe05a0000</link><description>黎巴嫩城市 91 人被杀四十多年后，一项新的调查证实了许多人的怀疑：这起真主党首次自杀式袭击是由一名什叶派恐怖分子驾驶一辆装满炸药的汽车发动的</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 21:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-04/ty-article/.premium/new-inquiry-refutes-original-israeli-probe-1982-tyre-disaster-was-terror-not-gas-blast/00000190-7a17-d3cb-a7ff-fb7fe05a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>